import React, { useRef, useState } from 'react'
import { Canvas, useFrame } from '@react-three/fiber'

import Camera from "./CamerSetup"
export default function ThreeIndex() {

    
    return (
        <Canvas>
          <Camera />

          <Boxes />

      )
}
